1
00:00:01,540 --> 00:00:06,700
 haynt iz JANUARY der fuftseter,

2
00:00:06,700 --> 00:00:08,966
nayntsn nayn zibn.

3
00:00:10,187 --> 00:00:14,860
mir nemen dem intervyu bay Mindl Melamed,

4
00:00:15,047 --> 00:00:17,083
un itst iz der TAPE numer tsvey.

5
00:00:18,680 --> 00:00:22,921
 ir hot zikh opgeshtelt oyf dem, az m'hot aykh ongehoybn fun plats traybn...

6
00:00:21,645 --> 00:00:24,980
m'hot undz ongehoybn traybn in der Ukrayne arayn.

7
00:00:25,240 --> 00:00:27,883
hot men undz arayngetribn keyn Molev...

8
00:00:28,362 --> 00:00:30,009
neyn, keyn Otik.

9
00:00:30,505 --> 00:00:33,110
arayngetribn in shtetele Otik,

10
00:00:33,110 --> 00:00:35,606
tsunoyfgenemen di vayber mit di kinder.

11
00:00:35,606 --> 00:00:37,460
s'hot shtark geregnt.

12
00:00:37,508 --> 00:00:40,117
m'iz gezesn bay dem Nester,

13
00:00:40,225 --> 00:00:42,736
vos m'hot undz gedarft aribershifn

14
00:00:42,736 --> 00:00:44,893
mit a paron keyn Molev.

15
00:00:45,338 --> 00:00:49,595
di vayber mit di kinder hot men arayngeleygt in shil arayn;

16
00:00:49,595 --> 00:00:51,890
oysgedishet gevorn dort.

17
00:00:52,307 --> 00:00:55,676
un di mener, un nokh mentshn, zenen geblibn

18
00:00:55,902 --> 00:00:59,980
bay der shil shteyn, vayl m'hot gedarft dortn ibernekhtikn.

19
00:01:00,390 --> 00:01:01,796
in der fri

20
00:01:01,796 --> 00:01:05,447
hot men aroysgenemen yedn eynem fun der, shil,

21
00:01:05,571 --> 00:01:08,349
un m'hot undz tsugetribn tsum Nester,

22
00:01:08,625 --> 00:01:12,650
un undz aribergeshift keyn Molev mit a paron,

23
00:01:12,650 --> 00:01:15,920
tsu bislekh di mentshn aribergeshift.

24
00:01:16,472 --> 00:01:20,170
mitn aribershifn iz undzers a FRIEND...

25
00:01:20,170 --> 00:01:22,215
er hot gehat a kranke shvester.

26
00:01:22,215 --> 00:01:23,638
er hot zi getrogn

27
00:01:23,678 --> 00:01:25,393
oyf di pleytses.

28
00:01:25,534 --> 00:01:27,553
iz tsugekumen a daytsh

29
00:01:27,677 --> 00:01:30,838
un er hot zi aropgerisn im fun di pleytses

30
00:01:30,838 --> 00:01:33,358
un arayngevarfn in Nester arayn,

31
00:01:33,364 --> 00:01:36,000
un undz geshift vayter.

32
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:38,450
mir zenen aribergekumen keyn Molev.

33
00:01:38,562 --> 00:01:42,488
zenen gezesn di daytshn oysgezetst in beyde zaytn,

34
00:01:42,645 --> 00:01:44,515
un zey hobn undz gezungen,

35
00:01:44,515 --> 00:01:46,504
"ir hot gevolt Stalinen?

36
00:01:46,645 --> 00:01:49,468
Stalin, Stalin," hobn zey undz gezungen,

37
00:01:49,468 --> 00:01:50,908
"hot ir Stalinen!"

38
00:01:51,268 --> 00:01:53,054
eyn alter daytsh...

39
00:01:53,054 --> 00:01:55,920
mayn mame hot getrogn a pitsele kind oyf di hent...

40
00:01:56,382 --> 00:02:00,100
hot er, iz er tsugekumen, hot im gegibn a shtikele broyt

41
00:02:00,178 --> 00:02:01,572
in hentl arayn,

42
00:02:02,254 --> 00:02:08,086
un er hot gemakht mitn kop vi eyner redt, "geyt vayter." un m'hot undz ongehoybn traybn oyf di vegn.

43
00:02:08,785 --> 00:02:14,340
undz arayngetribn tif in der Ukrayne arayn. m'hot undz durkhgetribn Yampele,

44
00:02:14,340 --> 00:02:16,946
m'hot undz durkhgetribn Zhmerinke,

45
00:02:17,813 --> 00:02:21,940
arayngetribn in Popovets, Kopaygorod.

46
00:02:22,774 --> 00:02:25,690
kh'gedenk nisht di shtet afile vosere.

47
00:02:25,963 --> 00:02:29,028
un in Popovets hot men undz geheysn,

48
00:02:29,507 --> 00:02:35,137
mir zol'mir blaybn do zitsn, oyf der gas, oys-... iz men geblibn zitsn oyf di vegn.

49
00:02:35,667 --> 00:02:39,272
un den hot men tseteylt di mentshn in budinek arayn.

50
00:02:40,830 --> 00:02:45,869
m'hot nisht gehat vu azoy fil mentshn ayntsuteyln. di froyen mit di kinder

51
00:02:45,943 --> 00:02:48,180
hot men aroyfgetribn in budinek,

52
00:02:48,525 --> 00:02:51,330
un di mener zenen dernokh nokhgekumen,

53
00:02:51,330 --> 00:02:53,002
un m'hot undz aruntergelozt

54
00:02:53,002 --> 00:02:54,357
hinter drotn.

55
00:02:55,528 --> 00:02:58,374
der budinek iz geven ⟨aza⟩ hoyz? vos ⟨iz dos geven⟩...?

56
00:02:56,811 --> 00:03:02,630
dos iz geven a groys plats vu di kolkhozn flegn trikenen

57
00:03:02,630 --> 00:03:05,545
di tatunen dortn, dem tabak,

58
00:03:05,822 --> 00:03:08,480
hobn di kolkhozn dortn getriknt.

59
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:09,596
s'iz geven

60
00:03:10,277 --> 00:03:12,481
a pol, a stelye,

61
00:03:12,538 --> 00:03:16,863
u- un ofn arum un arum, oyf slupes geshtanen dos.

62
00:03:16,863 --> 00:03:19,148
un do hot men undz arayngetribn.

63
00:03:19,643 --> 00:03:25,290
zeyer shver geven dortn tsu zayn. m'hot nit gehat vos tsu esn, m'iz geven hinter drotn.

64
00:03:26,511 --> 00:03:33,828
flegn tsukumen di goyim; vos m'hot no⟨r⟩ gehat, a mol hot men gekont epes baytn, un a mol hobn zey es oysgekhapt un zenen antlofn.

65
00:03:34,881 --> 00:03:39,910
un azoy hot men zikh dortn gemutshet bizkl s'hot ongehoybn vern groyse frest.

66
00:03:39,910 --> 00:03:42,772
m'hot nisht UNK sakh oysgefroyrn gevorn.

67
00:03:42,846 --> 00:03:47,690
m'hot nit gehat vos tsu esn. me fleg araynnemen zhmenyes mit shney,

68
00:03:47,690 --> 00:03:53,490
un mitn shney hot men gelebt; m'hot gelekt dem shney un dos iz geven der trunk un dos esn

69
00:03:53,490 --> 00:03:54,787
un alding.

70
00:03:55,401 --> 00:03:59,090
oyf a mol, az s'iz shoyn gevorn groys di frest,

71
00:03:59,090 --> 00:04:01,960
hot men aropgenemen di mentshn... vos er hot gehit,

72
00:04:02,252 --> 00:04:04,358
vos er hot gekukt oyfn lager...

73
00:04:04,358 --> 00:04:06,448
un m'hot oyfgemakht dem toyer.

74
00:04:07,365 --> 00:04:10,880
mayn m⟨u⟩ter iz ave- aroysgeganvet zikh

75
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,280
in a bay nakht

76
00:04:12,512 --> 00:04:17,399
oyf tsu betn epes, oystsubetn a shtikl broyt, az epes vos...

77
00:04:17,911 --> 00:04:21,520
iz zi gegangen noent, do vu mir ze'mir geven.

78
00:04:21,520 --> 00:04:23,430
hot men gegibn a bisl sholekhts,

79
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:25,854
m'hot gegibn a por bleter fun a berik.

80
00:04:25,995 --> 00:04:29,105
vos m- vos zi hot gekont, hot zi arayngebrakht un mir

81
00:04:29,105 --> 00:04:31,050
hobn mit dermit gelebt.

82
00:04:31,513 --> 00:04:34,139
den iz a froy geven dortn.

83
00:04:34,315 --> 00:04:36,148
zi hot gehat eyn meydele.

84
00:04:37,251 --> 00:04:45,650
un zi hot gezogt tsu mayn mamen... zi hot gezen vi me shtarbt far hunger, mentshn vern oysgefroyrn, hungerik...

85
00:04:46,043 --> 00:04:47,690
hot zi gezogt tsu mayn mamen,

86
00:04:47,832 --> 00:04:51,285
"efsher veln mir zikh aroysganvenen, un ir kumt mit mir,

87
00:04:51,325 --> 00:04:54,238
un ayere kinder zoln kukn tsu mayn kind,

88
00:04:54,885 --> 00:04:59,081
un me zol konen epes oysbetn az di kinder zoln hobn vos tsu esn."

89
00:04:59,661 --> 00:05:03,435
hot zi aroysgenemen mayn mamen mit mayn elterer shvester.

90
00:05:03,441 --> 00:05:06,287
"a kind," hot zi gezogt, "git men gikher

91
00:05:07,035 --> 00:05:08,660
a shtikele broyt."

92
00:05:08,723 --> 00:05:12,348
aroysgenemen, un hot zi avekgenemen in a dorf arayn,

93
00:05:12,348 --> 00:05:14,791
vos m'hot gezogt, dortn git men gut.

94
00:05:15,895 --> 00:05:19,551
s'iz geven mistome ⟨a⟩ tsen kilometer fun undzer lager.

95
00:05:19,928 --> 00:05:22,532
m'hot di mamen avekgenemen mit der shvester.

96
00:05:22,532 --> 00:05:25,035
s'iz oysgefaln a groyser shney.

97
00:05:25,429 --> 00:05:27,482
di mame hot nisht gekont aheymkumen.

98
00:05:29,175 --> 00:05:32,030
un zey zenen geblibn zitsn in vald,

99
00:05:32,095 --> 00:05:34,097
un azoy zenen zey gezesn

100
00:05:34,305 --> 00:05:36,790
biz zey hobn zikh tsugeshlept tsun a shtub,

101
00:05:37,073 --> 00:05:39,919
un hinter der shtub zenen zey geven a por tog,

102
00:05:41,207 --> 00:05:46,150
bizkl z- m'hot gemakht a steshke, az me zol konen geyn in vald, durkhn vald.

103
00:05:47,046 --> 00:05:48,862
ikh bin geblibn lign

104
00:05:48,902 --> 00:05:51,461
mit dem meydele un mit mayn bruderl.

105
00:05:51,923 --> 00:05:56,710
dos meydele hot gehat a koldere un mir hobn zikh aruntergerukt unter der koldere,

106
00:05:56,710 --> 00:05:59,030
me zol zikh onvaremen lebn ir.

107
00:05:59,263 --> 00:06:05,638
⟨ay⟩, ikh bin geven shoyn a groys meydl, hob ikh gevust⟨, darf araynnemen a⟩ bisl shney, gibn dem bruderl a bisl, un mir...

108
00:06:05,638 --> 00:06:08,083
oder zi iz geven nokh a kind.

109
00:06:08,933 --> 00:06:11,900
iz zi azoy lang gelign bizkl zi iz geshtorbn.

110
00:06:11,900 --> 00:06:16,588
mir ho'mir nit gevust. ikh bin gelign mit ir etlekhe tog unter der koldere,

111
00:06:16,695 --> 00:06:18,596
un zi iz geven geshtorbn.

112
00:06:19,783 --> 00:06:26,307
un lebn undz iz gelign tsvey shvesters: eyne iz geven a TEACHER un di andere veys ikh nit vos.

113
00:06:26,314 --> 00:06:29,820
geven, ⟨in⟩, far der milkhome a TEACHER.

114
00:06:29,820 --> 00:06:32,518
zogt zi tsu mir, "gib mir dayn bruderl.

115
00:06:33,047 --> 00:06:38,680
lomikh mit im aroysgeyn. m'vet oysbetn a por shtikelekh broyt, vet er dokh dir oykh aheymbrengen."

116
00:06:39,055 --> 00:06:41,130
zi hot genemen shmatkelekh

117
00:06:41,130 --> 00:06:43,942
un arumgeviklt mayn bruderl di fiselekh...

118
00:06:43,948 --> 00:06:46,540
er iz geven a kind fun fir yor...

119
00:06:47,340 --> 00:06:53,015
un hot im oyfgeneyt a torbele, ongeton oyfn haldz, un zi iz mit im aroysgegangen

120
00:06:53,015 --> 00:06:54,460
oyfn dorf.

121
00:06:56,284 --> 00:06:59,855
biz zi hot opgedankt der goye, hot er es oyfgegesn.

122
00:07:01,718 --> 00:07:09,410
etlekhe mol azoy. hot zi geklert, "loz er zikh onesn, un dernokh vet er shoyn konen tsunoyfleygn far undz oykh a por shtikelekh broyt."

123
00:07:10,392 --> 00:07:14,942
zi geyt mit im aroys fun der tsveyter, driter shtub. zogt zi, "Borele,

124
00:07:14,965 --> 00:07:17,299
du konst nit oyfesn in gantsn.

125
00:07:17,299 --> 00:07:21,100
du darfst aheymtrogn dayn shvesterl oykhet a shtikele broyt,

126
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:22,991
vayl zi vil oykhet esn."

127
00:07:23,402 --> 00:07:29,032
zey zenen arayngegan in shtub arayn tsu der goye betn epes, hot men im gegibn a shtikele broyt,

128
00:07:29,089 --> 00:07:31,395
arayngeleygt in torbele arayn.

129
00:07:32,177 --> 00:07:36,659
in etlekhe shtiber zenen zey gegangen, un dernokh iz zi mit im aheymgekumen.

130
00:07:36,885 --> 00:07:41,674
m'hot ayngeteylt di por shtikelekh broyt, mit a kartoflye, mit a berik

131
00:07:41,674 --> 00:07:43,860
ayngeteylt helft oyf helft:

132
00:07:43,860 --> 00:07:45,840
ikh hob gehat mitn bruderl

133
00:07:45,930 --> 00:07:49,653
shoyn a bisl, oyf a tsvey tog ⟨zikh⟩ gebahaltn shtikelekh,

134
00:07:50,773 --> 00:07:54,057
un zi hot gehat helft. den iz gekumen mayn mame.

135
00:07:54,891 --> 00:07:57,467
azoy vi der ployt iz shoyn geven ofn

136
00:07:58,215 --> 00:08:04,980
iz zi aropgegangen in shtot arayn. mayn mame iz geven zeyer a BOEVAYA froy, azoy...

137
00:08:05,505 --> 00:08:07,406
zi iz aropgegan in shtot arayn.

138
00:08:07,902 --> 00:08:11,811
m'hot shoyn gelozt aroysgeyn, hot zi gekont aropgeyn in shtot arayn.

139
00:08:11,884 --> 00:08:15,675
zi iz aropgegan in shtot arayn, hot zikh bagegnt mit mayn tatn's a khaver.

140
00:08:16,373 --> 00:08:18,881
er iz geven dort in der OBSHCHINe.

141
00:08:20,068 --> 00:08:21,610
hot zi im gezogt,

142
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:26,441
"Dovid, helf mir... nem mikh arop mit di kinder in shtot arayn,

143
00:08:26,447 --> 00:08:28,381
vayl me vert farfroyrn."

144
00:08:30,413 --> 00:08:34,001
hot er gezogt, er, er hot ir tsugezogt, er vet zi aropnemen.

145
00:08:34,260 --> 00:08:36,751
den, az di mame iz aheymgekumen...

146
00:08:37,212 --> 00:08:40,260
un dos bruderl mayns fun draytsn yor,

147
00:08:40,403 --> 00:08:45,375
gelign, er hot gornit geesn, farshishet gevorn, gevorn beyn, hoyt un beyn.

148
00:08:46,562 --> 00:08:49,441
un in der fri, me shteyt oyf: er iz toyt.

149
00:08:50,292 --> 00:08:53,740
der shney iz geven groys, efsher dray meter di heykh.

150
00:08:54,139 --> 00:08:56,900
shtark groyse shneyen iz oysgefaln.

151
00:08:58,307 --> 00:09:03,839
un di mame veys nisht vos tsu tun mit im. zi bet mentshn, me zol ir geyn helfn, me zol im

152
00:09:03,839 --> 00:09:05,726
ergets fargrobn.

153
00:09:05,968 --> 00:09:10,520
keyner vil nit geyn, un me ken nit geyn; m'iz hungerik, s'iz kalt.

154
00:09:10,778 --> 00:09:15,075
mir ho'mir gehat a zak vos me fleg im untershpreytn, m'iz oyf im geshlofn.

155
00:09:15,385 --> 00:09:17,410
hot zi genemen dem zak,

156
00:09:17,713 --> 00:09:23,326
genemen mayn bruderl, arayngeleygt di fis... der kop mit di hent hot im nokhgehongen...

157
00:09:23,805 --> 00:09:25,574
un genemen a lopete,

158
00:09:25,574 --> 00:09:31,380
un zi iz avekgegan in vald arayn. der vald, mir ze'mir dokh geven in vald, nor tifer a bisl.

159
00:09:31,433 --> 00:09:34,042
hot oysgegrobn a grub fun,

160
00:09:34,099 --> 00:09:35,696
funem shney,

161
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:40,010
un im aruntergeleygt untern shney, vayl s'iz geven farfroyrn

162
00:09:40,010 --> 00:09:42,140
un zi hot meyn nisht gekont.

163
00:09:42,402 --> 00:09:48,313
zi iz aheymgekumen, hot men zikh avekgezetst un m'hot zikh gut ongeveynt. zogt zi, "s'vet aropgeyn der shney,

164
00:09:48,313 --> 00:09:52,240
un di hint veln ayer bruder tseraysn oyf shtiklekh."

165
00:09:53,961 --> 00:09:56,587
un ken zayn, azoy iz dos take geven.

166
00:09:56,661 --> 00:10:00,941
s'iz durkhgegan a tsvey vokhn. di mame iz nokh a mol gegan in shtot arayn.

167
00:10:01,251 --> 00:10:05,870
vu er voynt, ot der khaver mayn tatn's, hot zi im nisht ge- nit gevust,

168
00:10:06,077 --> 00:10:07,910
nor zi hot ongehoybn fregn

169
00:10:08,389 --> 00:10:09,690
vu er voynt,

170
00:10:09,823 --> 00:10:12,150
mentshn, vu se voynt der un der.

171
00:10:12,150 --> 00:10:14,200
hot men ir gezogt, "do voynt er."

172
00:10:14,869 --> 00:10:18,980
zi iz arayngegan ahin. di vayb hot di mamen teykef derkent.

173
00:10:19,155 --> 00:10:21,461
hot er gezogt, "Rosye, ikh vel dir gibn...

174
00:10:21,805 --> 00:10:25,494
nem, breng arop di kinder. ikh'l dikh ergets araynrukn."

175
00:10:26,192 --> 00:10:33,620
in a sakh shtiber, in aza tsimer vi do iz geven fuftsn S- FAMILIES, akhtsn FAMILIES; m'iz gelign eyner oyfn andern.

176
00:10:32,790 --> 00:10:34,522
dortn iz oykh geven a geto?

177
00:10:34,562 --> 00:10:39,264
neyn, di shtot iz shoyn geven a fraye. dort hobn gevoynt di Ukrayner yidn,

178
00:10:40,266 --> 00:10:47,527
un s'iz shoyn geven aroysgekumen mentshn fun d⟨UNK⟩ shoyn nisht geven keyn geto. di geto iz geven oyfn budinek,

179
00:10:47,527 --> 00:10:48,987
aroys der shtot.

180
00:10:48,987 --> 00:10:52,090
in der ⟨BEGINNING⟩, vi azoy m'hot undz gefirt fun di vegn,

181
00:10:52,090 --> 00:10:54,418
hot men undz aroyfgefirt in der geto arayn.

182
00:10:54,762 --> 00:10:59,540
un dernokh dem hot men zikh tsu bislekh ongehoybn aroysshlepn fun der geto.

183
00:10:58,862 --> 00:11:00,999
un keyn vakh iz shoyn nit geven?

184
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:02,214
s'iz shoyn nisht geven di vakh.

185
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,324
ven iz dos geven, in velkhn yor?

186
00:11:02,457 --> 00:11:05,606
di vakh iz nit geven. in di groyse frestn

187
00:11:06,169 --> 00:11:12,798
zenen di vakh antrunen gevorn. zey hobn nisht gevolt zitsn dortn. ver vet zitsn? zey zenen aropgegan in shtot arayn,

188
00:11:12,798 --> 00:11:16,541
zenen geven in shtot. m'hot in shtot oykhet undz genug geton.

189
00:11:17,644 --> 00:11:23,426
s'iz geven di Rumener un s'iz geven a por daytshn, nisht keyn sakh daytshn; meystn teyl Rumener iz geven.

190
00:11:25,002 --> 00:11:28,843
iz er gegangen un hot undz arayngezetst in a shtub arayn,

191
00:11:29,592 --> 00:11:33,098
efsher tsvey meter. mir ze'mir geven,

192
00:11:33,098 --> 00:11:35,222
ze'mir geven a zeks mentshn,

193
00:11:35,515 --> 00:11:38,361
in a, in a CORNER, in a vinkl

194
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:40,042
⟨undz aroy-⟩ dortn.

