409
00:22:19,498 --> 00:22:24,976
ales in di vegn, ales oyf d-... mir ze'mir geven nor oyf vegn.

410
00:22:25,152 --> 00:22:29,179
mir hobn keyn shtiber nisht gezen. undz hot men getribn durkh felder.

411
00:22:29,185 --> 00:22:32,098
durkh felder un durkh velder hot men undz getribn.

412
00:22:32,543 --> 00:22:36,033
m'hot keyn shtiber nisht gezen. tsu yedn dorf noent

413
00:22:36,033 --> 00:22:38,610
iz ts- iz men tsugekumen mit di mentshn,

414
00:22:38,610 --> 00:22:42,140
iz shoyn gevartet andere Rumener mit, mit daytshn.

415
00:22:42,140 --> 00:22:44,760
m'hot ibergenemen; zey hobn undz gefirt vayter.

416
00:22:43,798 --> 00:22:46,289
a, aykh hobn bavakht Rumener?

417
00:22:45,570 --> 00:22:47,570
Rumener mit daytshn.

418
00:22:47,250 --> 00:22:48,250
mit daytshn.

419
00:22:48,557 --> 00:22:54,491
