421
00:22:57,619 --> 00:22:59,690
un m'hot zey geshosn dernokh,

422
00:22:59,256 --> 00:23:00,920
ir hot gezen azelkhe?

423
00:22:59,690 --> 00:23:01,590
di vos zey hobn nit gekont geyn.

424
00:23:01,298 --> 00:23:02,540
ir hot gezen?

425
00:23:01,590 --> 00:23:05,190
az m'hot undz getribn dos ershte mol in der Ukrayne arayn,

426
00:23:05,770 --> 00:23:08,734
un m'iz opgeven in der Ukrayne a yor,

427
00:23:08,773 --> 00:23:12,238
un dernokh dem hot men undz krikgetribn keyn Basarabye,

428
00:23:12,238 --> 00:23:13,931
demlt hob ikh gezen

429
00:23:14,005 --> 00:23:17,250
az mentshn alte zenen gelign in di kanaves.

430
00:23:17,250 --> 00:23:19,756
ven m'hot undz getribn far Sukeran

431
00:23:19,756 --> 00:23:21,963
iz arayngegan di Khotiner.

432
00:23:22,206 --> 00:23:23,680
di Khotiner hot men arayn-....

433
00:23:23,680 --> 00:23:26,165
in Sukeran ze'mir geven hinter drotn.

434
00:23:27,167 --> 00:23:30,041
krikgetribn funem ershtn mol

435
00:23:30,041 --> 00:23:31,475
fun der Ukrayne.

436
00:23:31,475 --> 00:23:33,826
zenen mir gekumen; far dem

437
00:23:34,660 --> 00:23:37,280
shtetele Sukeran iz gelign

438
00:23:37,280 --> 00:23:40,440
a fir, finef mentshn, eltere,

439
00:23:40,735 --> 00:23:44,863
un lebn zey iz geshtanen di goyim. m'hot gekopet griber.

440
00:23:45,072 --> 00:23:47,529
hobn zey ongehoybn tsun undz shrayen,

441
00:23:47,586 --> 00:23:50,291
mir zol'mir zey tsuvarfn a por shteyner,

442
00:23:50,291 --> 00:23:53,115
az zey zoln zikh konen aleyn hargenen,

443
00:23:53,188 --> 00:23:57,012
az me zol zey nisht araynleygn lebedikerheyt in grub arayn.

444
00:23:57,323 --> 00:23:58,910
dos hob ikh gezen.

445
00:23:58,892 --> 00:24:00,658
vi hobn zey gebetn, oyf yidish?

446
00:24:00,040 --> 00:24:05,872
oyf yidish! yidishe mentshn, yidishe eltere mentshn. zey hobn shoyn nisht gekont geyn,

447
00:24:06,199 --> 00:24:09,267
iz hobn zey gebetn, me zol zey tsuvarfn shteyner.

448
00:24:09,267 --> 00:24:13,098
un ven m'hot undz getribn krik dos tsveyte m- dos ershte mol,

449
00:24:13,098 --> 00:24:16,233
hot men undz getribn in ⟨Rublenevitser⟩ vald,

450
00:24:16,712 --> 00:24:19,034
arayngetribn in a vald arayn.

451
00:24:19,210 --> 00:24:21,026
geven mentshn,

452
00:24:22,163 --> 00:24:25,280
himl un erd. fun ile shtet

453
00:24:25,280 --> 00:24:28,704
iz geven dort in dem ⟨Rublenevitser⟩ vald di mentshn.

454
00:24:30,803 --> 00:24:32,749
s'iz geven groyse hitsn.

455
00:24:32,749 --> 00:24:37,499
m'hot gemakht kolibes fun shtiker beymer, vayl s'iz geven a vald, hot men opgebrokhn

456
00:24:37,499 --> 00:24:40,719
un m'hot gemakht azoy ko⟨UNK⟩ kolibes.

457
00:24:40,843 --> 00:24:43,649
oyfn veg hot mayn mame farbitn a kleydl

458
00:24:43,649 --> 00:24:44,688
bay a goye

459
00:24:44,688 --> 00:24:46,929
far a finef kilo tsuker.

460
00:24:47,340 --> 00:24:50,624
mit dem tsuker ho'mir gelebt tsvey khadoshim

461
00:24:50,648 --> 00:24:54,523
in dem vald, UNK in ⟨Rublenevitser⟩ vald.

462
00:24:55,626 --> 00:25:00,690
un s'hot shoyn ongehoybn vern di frest, un ongehoybn nokh a mol regenen osyen.

463
00:25:01,093 --> 00:25:06,791
iz gor in plutsem... me zitst azoy in di velder. m'hot geveynt un geklogt; vos hot men gehat tsu tun?

464
00:25:06,949 --> 00:25:10,230
mir ho'mir gehat dos bisl tsuker, tsvey lefl tsuker,

465
00:25:10,230 --> 00:25:12,450
hot di mame gemakht a gantsn kesl vaser

466
00:25:12,450 --> 00:25:16,810
un undz gegibn zis vaser tsu trinken. dos hot men gekont, meyn gornisht.

467
00:25:17,428 --> 00:25:22,108
mayn mame's shvester hot zikh aroysgeganvet funem vald, mit a kind tsugebunen

468
00:25:22,108 --> 00:25:24,088
oyfn haldz, a kleyn kind,

469
00:25:24,516 --> 00:25:27,530
un zi hot ge- oysgebetn a por shtiklekh broyt.

470
00:25:28,296 --> 00:25:34,760
hot men zi gekhapt un zi iz aray- m'hot zi arayngebrakht in lager arayn, un dos broyt hot men tsevarfn

471
00:25:34,911 --> 00:25:38,434
in droysn aroys, nisht dort vu di mentshn zenen geven,

472
00:25:38,434 --> 00:25:42,211
un m'hot zi azoy geshlogn az zi iz geven shvarts vi ayere PANTS.

473
00:25:43,315 --> 00:25:44,451
un azoy ⟨sh-⟩

474
00:25:44,451 --> 00:25:47,910
hot shoyn moyre gehat di mentshn aroystsugeyn fun vald.

475
00:25:48,276 --> 00:25:50,177
s'hot gedirt a por tog.

476
00:25:50,250 --> 00:25:51,800
me tut a kuk:

477
00:25:51,800 --> 00:25:54,682
se kumen tsu a akht rayters

478
00:25:54,688 --> 00:25:56,090
oyf di ferd,

479
00:25:57,253 --> 00:26:00,858
un me zogt, ile Lipkaner zoln aroysgeyn fun vald.

480
00:26:02,721 --> 00:26:06,427
m'hot undz aroysgenemen fun vald. m'hot undz ongehoybn firn

481
00:26:07,429 --> 00:26:12,710
keyn Basa- in Basarabye, keyn Basarabye. m'hot undz arayngefirt far dem Sukeran,

482
00:26:12,710 --> 00:26:14,944
dos vos kh'hob aykh dertseylt fun di mentshn.

483
00:26:14,944 --> 00:26:18,881
mir ze'mir geven in Sukeran in a lager, hinter drotn.

484
00:26:19,748 --> 00:26:20,805
un den,

485
00:26:21,132 --> 00:26:24,560
eyn mol bay nakht, a Khotiner yunger-man

486
00:26:24,560 --> 00:26:27,180
geyt arum in ile shtiber un shrayt,

487
00:26:27,180 --> 00:26:31,453
"Zeydl's beker's vayb iz do? fun Zeydl beker iz emetser geblibn?"

488
00:26:33,197 --> 00:26:40,346
