489
00:26:40,926 --> 00:26:42,725
"Zeydl's vayb iz do."

490
00:26:42,816 --> 00:26:46,202
"vu iz zi? in vosere shtub?" er hot undz opgezukht.

491
00:26:46,545 --> 00:26:50,437
er iz arumgegan a gantse nakht, er hot undz gezukht, mayn tatn's a khaver.

492
00:26:51,152 --> 00:26:53,663
un er hot getrogn a opgekokhte...

493
00:26:53,663 --> 00:26:56,709
ikh veys nit tsi ir v- ir veyst vos heyst a mamelige.

494
00:26:56,709 --> 00:27:00,430
fun, k- gele, fun papshoyes mel.

495
00:27:00,430 --> 00:27:04,781
opgekokht, ayngeviklt in a hantekh un ⟨es⟩ getrogn un er hot undz gezukht.

496
00:27:06,407 --> 00:27:10,884
iz arayngekumen, er hot derzen mayn mamen un m'hot geveynt gut ile.

497
00:27:10,884 --> 00:27:12,847
hot undz gegibn, me zol opesn.

498
00:27:12,972 --> 00:27:15,812
er iz shoyn dortn geven. er iz a Khotiner geven.

499
00:27:15,812 --> 00:27:19,250
zey zenen geven frirert. zey hot nisht getribn keynem

500
00:27:19,250 --> 00:27:21,828
tsvey mol in, der Ukrayne arayn.

501
00:27:21,828 --> 00:27:24,182
getribn hot men getribn di Lipkaner,

502
00:27:24,182 --> 00:27:27,022
far derfar vos di Lipkaner komunistn

503
00:27:27,265 --> 00:27:29,413
zenen tsugegan tsu der brik

504
00:27:29,413 --> 00:27:31,882
ven di Rumener hobn gedarft antloyfn.

505
00:27:32,614 --> 00:27:34,126
in v- in velkhn yor iz dos geven?

506
00:27:33,390 --> 00:27:35,088
in fertsikstn yor.

507
00:27:35,668 --> 00:27:40,922
un zey hobn opgerisn di Rumener di pagonen, m'hot zey bashpign... di komunistn...

508
00:27:40,922 --> 00:27:43,715
hobn zey gezogt, "mir vel'mir krikkumen,

509
00:27:43,715 --> 00:27:46,230
vel'mir zikh mit aykh oprekhenen."

510
00:27:46,230 --> 00:27:48,260
far derfar iz undzer shtot

511
00:27:48,260 --> 00:27:50,883
gegangen tsvey mol in der Ukrayne arayn.

512
00:27:51,295 --> 00:27:56,452
di ile shtetlekh zenen eyn mol gegangen, un Lipkan hot men getribn tsvey mol.

513
00:27:56,830 --> 00:27:59,895
durkh di komunistn, vos zey hobn azoy geton.

514
00:28:00,002 --> 00:28:04,873
dem ershtn mol hot men aykh getribn fun eyn un fertsikstn yor, fun JULY

515
00:28:02,888 --> 00:28:05,163
funem eyn un fertsikst-... yo.

516
00:28:05,031 --> 00:28:06,223
biz...?

517
00:28:06,094 --> 00:28:09,077
m'hot undz getribn oyf di vegn in der Ukrayne arayn.

518
00:28:08,997 --> 00:28:11,117
