00:28:25,939 --> 00:28:27,502
un dem ershtn mol?

528
00:28:28,610 --> 00:28:31,130
ahin undz getribn, un krikgetribn,

529
00:28:31,130 --> 00:28:34,050
un dernokh krikgetribn oyf dem zelbn plats.

530
00:28:34,326 --> 00:28:37,273
